description: Alan is ready for his first time. He thinks about going to the gay bar down the block and picking-up some random. But he wants it done right, so he calls his friend Ayden. Alan knows Ayden has had his fair share of experience and he will do the job right. It doesnt take Ayden long to come over. Before you know it he has Alan bent over and giving him what he wanted.
title: Cock Wise
